passiveSkills.name: Absolute Zero
passiveSkills.desc: Fixed chance of inflicting Freeze when hitting an enemy with an Advanced Skill.

advancedSkills.name_text_id: エンハンスアーマメント

advancedSkills.name: Ice Lance Onslaught
advancedSkills.desc: Sends forth a wave of ice lances along the ground. Deals Water damage and has a chance to freeze. In EA mode, the range expands.

advancedSkills.name: Freezing Field
advancedSkills.desc: Creates a cold zone in front of you. Deals damage over time to enemies inside the zone and has a chance of freezing them. Radius is wider in EA mode.

advancedSkills.name: Rage Spike
advancedSkills.desc: Rush towards the enemy and perform a sweeping attack. In EA mode, ice spears shoot out from the ground in conjunction with the sweeping attack.

advancedSkills.name: Ice Lance Onslaught
advancedSkills.desc: Sends forth a wave of ice lances along the ground. Deals Water damage and has a chance to freeze. In EA mode, the range expands.

advancedSkills.name: Release Recollection
advancedSkills.desc: Unleash your weapon's power to damage enemies in a wide area around you. Deals Water damage. Guaranteed to freeze.

advancedSkills.name: Heavy Attack
advancedSkills.desc: Stronger than a Normal Attack. Use after a Normal Attack combo to branch into a Combo Finish. Hold to use Ice Discharge, to fire ice bullets.
